# Metta AI - Multi-agent RL project

## Key paths
- `metta/` - Core Python (agents, RL, simulation)
- `mettagrid/` - C++/Python environment

## Commands  
- Always use `uv run` for Python
- Setup: `./install.sh`, Test: `metta test`, Lint: `metta lint --fix`

## Recipe system
```bash
uv run ./tools/run.py experiments.recipes.arena.train run=name
uv run ./tools/run.py experiments.recipes.arena.evaluate policy_uri=file://./checkpoints
```

## After Python edits - ALWAYS:
```bash
ruff format [file_path] && ruff check --fix [file_path]
```